title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VII Australia - Photogrammetry Cairns
description:
It has been released: World Update VII Australia. In this video we will do our fifth flight above Australia and we are going to visit Cairns this time. Cairns received a photogrammetry update but no POI's, at least not in the city itself. In front of the coast however there are 2 POI's:

- Great Barrier Reef
- Green Island Jetty
